title: Suicides in Sweden in 2018 , by gender and age group
summary: Overall Men, and Women are gradually decreasing,  throughout the Year
The order of lines according to average values of Number of suicides in per 100 thousands, in descending order is: 1. Men, and lastly, 2. Women.
The difference of Number of suicides in per 100 thousands between Men and Women is smaller at Year 75_years_and_older compared to the Year 15-44_years.
